name: #79 Lilira
description: The eye moved around as though examining the cave and then centered, looking straight at the three renegades. Another rumble occurred, causing a stalactite to fall right between them, making them separate from each other. Then, under the eye, another line formed and it opened, uttering the words, 'I we Lilira na I yakkhis realm, i goddess na wants, BLINNYU ya!'\n\n[Season 2, Bonus Chapter - Renegades](https://eyeverse.world/renegades)
